#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&blinken; is based on an electronic game released in 1978, which challenges "
"players to remember sequences of increasing length. On the face of the "
"device, there are 4 different color buttons, each one with their own "
"distinctive sound. These buttons light up randomly, creating the sequence "
"that the player must then recall. If the player is successful in remembering "
"the sequence of lights in the correct order, they advance to the next stage, "
"where an identical sequence with one extra step is presented. If they are "
"incorrect, the game is lost, and the player must start again from the "
"beginning. The goal is to get a high score - each step in the sequence is "
"worth one point, so correct entry of a sequence of 8 lights is worth 8 "
"points on the high score table."
msgstr ""
"&blinken; temelji na elektronski igri, izdani leta 1978, ki igralce izziva, "
"da si zapomnijo vse daljša zaporedja. Na sprednji strani naprave so 4 "
"različni barvni gumbi, vsak s svojim značilnim zvokom. Ti gumbi zasvetijo "
"naključno in ustvarijo zaporedje, ki ga mora igralec nato priklicati. Če si "
"igralec uspe zapomniti zaporedje luči v pravilnem vrstnem redu, napreduje na "
"naslednjo stopnjo, kjer je predstavljeno enako zaporedje z enim dodatnim "
"korakom. Če so nepravilne, je igra izgubljena in igralec mora začeti znova "
"od začetka. Cilj je doseči visoko oceno - vsak korak v zaporedju je vreden "
"eno točko, zato je pravilen vnos zaporedja 8 lučk vreden 8 točk na tabeli z "
"najboljšimi rezultati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &blinken;"
msgstr "Uporaba &blinken;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &blinken;, showing the "
"general interface to the application. Most of the screen is taken up by the "
"<interface>device</interface>, with the <interface>4 colored buttons</"
"interface>, with the device controls (<interface>score counter</interface>, "
"<guibutton>Start</guibutton> button, &etc;) in the center of the screen. The "
"current status of the application is displayed on the <interface>piece of "
"paper</interface> under the device. In the corners of the application, there "
"are 3 buttons:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je zaslon, ki se prikaže ob zagonu &blinken; in prikazuje splošni "
"vmesnik za aplikacijo. Večino zaslona zavzema <interface>naprava</"
"interface>, s <interface>4 barvnimi gumbi</interface>, s kontrolniki "
"naprave(<interface>števec rezultatov</interface>, <guibutton>Start </"
"guibutton> &etc;) na sredini zaslona. Trenutno stanje aplikacije je "
"prikazano na <interface>kosu papirja</interface> pod napravo. V vogalih "
"aplikacije so 3 gumbi:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &blinken;</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Tukaj je zaslon, ki se prikaže ob zagonu &blinken;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &blinken;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Tu je zaslon, ki se prikaže ob zagonu &blinken;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Highscores</guibutton> button <action>opens a dialog that "
"displays the <guilabel>Highscores</guilabel> table</action> for each of the "
"3 difficulty levels (the <guilabel>Highscores</guilabel> table can also be "
"accessed by <action>clicking on the <interface>score counter</interface>)</"
"action>:"
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Rezultati</guibutton> <action>odpre pogovorno okno, ki "
"prikaže tabelo <guilabel>Rezultati</guilabel></action> za vsako od 3 "
"težavnostnih stopenj (tabela <guilabel>Rezultati</guilabel> lahko dostopate "
"tudi tako, da <action>kliknete na <interface>števec rezultatov</interface>)</"
"action>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo><guibutton>Highscores</guibutton> button</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo><guibutton>Gumb za najboljše rezultate</guibutton></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase><guibutton>Highscores</guibutton> button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gumb <guibutton>Najboljši rezultati</guibutton></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Quit</guibutton> button <action>closes the application</"
"action>:"
msgstr "Gumb <guibutton>Izhod</guibutton> <action>zapre aplikacijo</action>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo><guibutton>Quit</guibutton> button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gumb <guibutton>Zapri</guibutton></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase><guibutton>Quit</guibutton> button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><guibutton>Zapri</guibutton> gumb</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Help</guibutton> button is special, in that it "
"<action>reveals 4 sub-buttons</action>. These buttons are shown when the "
"<guibutton>Help</guibutton> button is <action>hovered over</action>, and "
"provide access to the <guilabel>&blinken; Handbook</guilabel> (this "
"document), <guilabel>Show/Hide Settings</guilabel>, and the <guilabel>About "
"&blinken;</guilabel> and <guilabel>About &kde;</guilabel> dialogs:"
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton> je poseben, ker <action>razkrije 4 "
"podgumbe</action>. Ti gumbi so prikazani, ko gumb <guibutton>Pomoč</"
"guibutton> premaknete <action>nad</action>, in omogočajo dostop do "
"<guilabel>&blinken; Priročnik</guilabel> (ta dokument), <guilabel>Pokaži/"
"skrij nastavitve</guilabel> in pogovorni okni <guilabel>O &blinken;</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>O &kde;</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo><guibutton>Help</guibutton> button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gumb <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase><guibutton>Help</guibutton> button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase><guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton> gumb</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To become familiar with the workings of the game, you can interact with the "
"<interface>colored buttons</interface> whilst on the main screen. The "
"buttons will illuminate and produce a tone upon being pressed."
msgstr ""
"Če se želite seznaniti z delovanjem igre, lahko na glavnem zaslonu "
"uporabljate <interface>barvne gumbe</interface>. Gumbi bodo ob pritisku "
"zasvetili in oddali ton."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a Game"
msgstr "Zagon igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are familiar with the workings of the application, a game can be "
"started by pressing the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> button in the center of "
"the screen. This <quote>powers on</quote> the device, as shown by the "
"illuminated <interface>score counter</interface>. You can then "
"<action>choose the difficulty level</action> that you want to attempt:"
msgstr ""
"Ko se seznanite z delovanjem aplikacije, lahko igro začnete s pritiskom "
"gumba <guibutton>Začni</guibutton> na sredini zaslona. To <quote>vklopi</"
"quote> napravo, kot prikazuje osvetljeni <interface>števec rezultatov</"
"interface>. Nato lahko <action>izberete težavnostno stopnjo</action>, ki jo "
"želite preizkusiti:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select difficulty level</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izberite težavnostno stopnjo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select difficulty level</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izberi težavnostno stopnjo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are 3 levels in &blinken;:"
msgstr "V &blinken; so 3 ravni:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Level 1 is the easiest level, as it provides the longest time break between "
"each sequence playback."
msgstr ""
"1. stopnja je najlažja stopnja, saj zagotavlja najdaljši časovni premor med "
"vsakim predvajanjem zaporedja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Level 2 is the intermediate level. It is identical to the previous level, "
"but has a smaller time break between each sequence playback."
msgstr ""
"2. stopnja je srednja stopnja. Je enaka prejšnji stopnji, vendar ima manjši "
"časovni premor med vsakim predvajanjem zaporedja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Level ? is the most difficult level of &blinken;. It takes the timings from "
"Level 2, but each sequence is totally random, rather than following on from "
"the previous sequence, as in the standard game type."
msgstr ""
"Stopnja ? je najtežja stopnja &blinken;. Vzame časovne razporede od 2. "
"stopnje, vendar je vsako zaporedje popolnoma naključno, namesto da sledi "
"prejšnjemu zaporedju, kot pri standardni vrsti igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering a New Highscore"
msgstr "Vnos novega najboljšega rezultata"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are lucky enough to get a highscore, it will be entered into the "
"<guilabel>Highscores</guilabel> table. A dialog will ask for a name to "
"associate with your score in the table:"
msgstr ""
"Če imate srečo in dobite najboljši rezultat, bo ta vnesen v tabelo "
"<guilabel>Rezultati</guilabel>. Pogovorno okno bo zahtevalo ime, ki bo "
"povezano z vašim rezultatom v tabeli:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Highscore nickname prompt dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno s pozivom za vzdevek najboljših točk</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Highscore nickname prompt dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za vzdevek z najboljšim rezultatom</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only 5 scores are kept for each level, so try not to be disappointed if you "
"don't make it!"
msgstr ""
"Za vsako stopnjo se hrani samo 5 rezultatov, zato poskusite ne biti "
"razočarani, če vam ne uspe!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing Tips"
msgstr "Nasveti za igranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&blinken; is the ultimate memory game, though you need not possess the "
"ultimate memory to be successful. These tips will help you in your pursuit "
"of the best score:"
msgstr ""
"&blinken; je ultimativna igra spomina, čeprav vam za uspeh ni treba imeti "
"ultimativnega spomina. Ti nasveti vam bodo pomagali doseči najboljši "
"rezultat:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have PC speakers, turn them on with the sound at a good level so that "
"you can hear the tones alongside seeing the flashing lights."
msgstr ""
"Če imate računalniške zvočnike, jih vključite z dobro glasnostjo, da boste "
"poleg utripajočih lučk slišali zvoke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Experiment with both the mouse and <link linkend=\"accessibility\">keyboard</"
"link> interaction methods, to see which one suites your memory best."
msgstr ""
"Eksperimentirajte z načinoma interakcije z miško in <link linkend="
"\"accessibility\">tipkovnico</link>, da vidite, kateri najbolj ustreza "
"vašemu spominu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try remembering the sequence as a list of colors."
msgstr "Poskusite si zapomniti zaporedje kot seznam barv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try remembering the sequence as positions on the screen."
msgstr "Poskusite si zapomniti zaporedje kot položaje na zaslonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accessibility Options"
msgstr "Možnosti dostopnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To allow &blinken; to be more easily enjoyed by certain users, there are "
"several accessibility options built into &blinken;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dovoliti &blinken; Da bi ga nekateri uporabniki lažje uporabljali, "
"je v &blinken; vgrajenih več možnosti dostopnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and modify the accessibility options of &blinken;, press the &Ctrl; "
"key (whilst a game is not in progress):"
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati in spremeniti možnosti dostopnosti &blinken;, "
"pritisnite &Ctrl; ključ (medtem ko igra ni v teku):"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&blinken; access keys</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&blinken; dostopne tipke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&blinken; access keys</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&blinken; dostopne tipke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "To return to the game screen, press the &Ctrl; key again."
msgstr "Za vrnitev na zaslon igre pritisnite &Ctrl; ponovno ključ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alongside use of the mouse, &blinken; also allows the user to operate the "
"game using the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Poleg uporabe miške, &blinken; uporabniku omogoča tudi upravljanje igre s "
"tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keys are <keycap>1</keycap>, <keycap>2</keycap>, <keycap>3</keycap>, "
"<keycap>4</keycap> by default."
msgstr ""
"Tipke so privzeto <keycap>1</keycap>, <keycap>2</keycap>, <keycap>3</"
"keycap>, <keycap>4</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the mapping of any button, click it using the mouse. It will then "
"be highlighted, waiting for input. Press the desired key on the keyboard to "
"change the currently assigned key."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti preslikavo katerega koli gumba, ga kliknite z miško. "
"Nato bo označeno in čaka na vnos. Pritisnite želeno tipko na tipkovnici, da "
"spremenite trenutno dodeljeno tipko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are other options available in the middle of the window: "
"<interface>Sounds</interface> and <interface>Font</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Na sredini okna so na voljo še druge možnosti: <interface>Zvoki</interface> "
"in <interface>Pisava</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By unchecking the <interface>Sounds</interface> checkbox, the &blinken; "
"sound effects will be suppressed."
msgstr ""
"Če počistite potrditveno polje <interface>Sounds</interface>, se &blinken; "
"zvočni učinki bodo izključeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By unchecking the <interface>Font</interface> checkbox, a standard font will "
"be used for status text instead of the default handwriting font."
msgstr ""
"Če počistite potrditveno polje <interface>Pisava</interface>, bo za besedilo "
"statusa namesto privzete pisave rokopisa uporabljena standardna pisava."

